Package ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types

Interface ImyhatFunction<R>

Type Parameters:
R - the output type that will result from the conversion
All Known Implementing Classes:
AsJsonNode
public interface ImyhatFunction<R>
Convert a value based on the provided information

In some cases, a Shesmu value may be passed to Java as Object and an accompanying Imyhat. This interface allows converting the value into more specific values and returning a common result.

See Also:
